Daimler’s Mercedes to Hire 1,250 Workers in Brazil, Argentina

-- B y   R a j i v   S e k h r i
-- 
2011-06-30T18:00:00Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-30/daimler-s-mercedes-to-hire-1-250-workers-in-brazil-argentina.html
Daimler AG (DAI) ’s Mercedes-Benz
trucks unit will hire 1,250 workers this year for assembly
plants in  Brazil  and  Argentina , the company said in an e-mailed
statement today.  Mercedes-Benz Trucks expects to exceed sales volume of
200,000 vehicles in Brazil by 2020, the statement said. The unit
sold 162,000 trucks in 2010.  To contact the reporter responsible for this story:
